Sentencas: Decreasing the working temperature of solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) to 400 degrees C-600 degrees C is a primary concern for current fuel cell research.
Titulo: Development of conducting Bi0.5Sr0.5FeO3-δ-Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ composite cathodes for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: Unfortunately decrease in operating temperatures leads to increase in cathode po-larization, which deteriorates electrochemical activity of the cathode for oxygen reduction reaction (ORR).
Titulo: Development of conducting Bi0.5Sr0.5FeO3-δ-Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ composite cathodes for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: Consequently, the search of new cathode materials is one of the critical bottle-neck towards the development of intermediate-temperature SOFCs (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Development of conducting Bi0.5Sr0.5FeO3-δ-Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ composite cathodes for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: In this study, we have successfully synthesized Bi0.5Sr0.5FeO3_delta and Bi0.5Sr0.5FeO3_delta-Gd0.1Ce0.9O2_delta((1-x) BSFO-xGDC) composite cathodes with varying compositions (x = 50, 40, 30, and 20wt%).
Titulo: Development of conducting Bi0.5Sr0.5FeO3-δ-Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ composite cathodes for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The crystal structure, microstructure, electrochemical properties and performance stability of these composite cathodes have been comprehensively evaluated using techniques such as X-ray diffraction (XRD), scanning electron microscopy (SEM) and electrochemical impedance spectroscopy (EIS).
Titulo: Development of conducting Bi0.5Sr0.5FeO3-δ-Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ composite cathodes for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: Our results demonstrate that the introduction of Gd0.1Ce0.9O2_delta( GDC) has a significant impact on the electrochemical performance of the composite cathodes.
Titulo: Development of conducting Bi0.5Sr0.5FeO3-δ-Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ composite cathodes for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: Among the different compositions studied, the cathode with a compo-sition of x = 70 wt% exhibits particularly promising electrochemical properties.
Titulo: Development of conducting Bi0.5Sr0.5FeO3-δ-Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ composite cathodes for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The electrode resistance po-larization of 70BiSFO-30GDC is 0.39 omega cm2 and 0.8 omega cm2 for symmetrical and half-cell at 600 degrees C.
Titulo: Development of conducting Bi0.5Sr0.5FeO3-δ-Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ composite cathodes for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The preliminary results of this study reveal that the 70BiSFO-30GDC composite cathode demonstrates remarkable ORR activity.
Titulo: Development of conducting Bi0.5Sr0.5FeO3-δ-Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ composite cathodes for IT-SOFCs
